title: Shocking Stats + Super Bowl Reactions, Cooper Kupp-It!- Fantasy Football Podcast for 2/15
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode!! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason reveal and react to shocking stats from the 2021 fantasy football season! Plus, a Super Bowl recap, the latest NFL News, and more! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for February 15th, 2022.
The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(11:25) - NFL News
(20:25) - Shocking Stats
(20:40) - Minnesota Vikings
(25:10) - Inside the 5
(30:55) - Jalen Hurts
